<h2>Bonanza!!</h2>
What is Bonanza?? Bonanza was the second longest running TV westerns in color!!
It ran for 14 seasons from 1959 to 1973! Bonanza was on the tail of Gunsmoke,
with 14 years of 14 seasons, while Gunsmoke is filmed for over 20 years!!
